{"tid":1792361,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"邊個仆街喺我面前自稱連登仔.....，見一個我便消滅一個....","createTime":"2019-12-21T14:49:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T02:52:54.000Z","uid":45787,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"012235e22ced0ec7cfa2bb8054ad989c830fecaa","tid":1792361,"uid":45787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T14:49:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z2VDoDv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz2VDoDv.png&h=0b248d1c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qMJJzLb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqMJJzLb.jpg&h=7dcf4b40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/khkevinwong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkhkevinwong&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3PSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=c3974deb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/khkevinwong</a>"},{"pid":"bf0745aa0ea1fbcaebebd418ae9f2d99aa84ac84","tid":1792361,"uid":147916,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T14:53:36.000Z","msg":"葉問生canncer，去美國幫仔搵學校，打贏晒班歧視支那人嘅鬼佬，同時李小龍既徒弟係美國得罪軍官，但軍官挑葉問機但打輸左，最後葉問返香港教仔詠春然後死咗。"},{"pid":"5ebf7f86395cf9fb68edb346c69f03ea9e62f9d6","tid":1792361,"uid":145273,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T14:53:53.000Z","msg":"連登有成十幾萬人，你慢慢消滅飽佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84bee6d2886e3e1d8df7d5e5bb535201b89341ae","tid":1792361,"uid":145273,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T14:54:17.000Z","msg":"#不是劇透 #必須看到尾<br />\n#入戲院前你要知的小背景<br />\n<br />\n【無雷】你不能不知道的＜葉問4＞基礎認識<br />\n<br />\n葉問得了癌症，偏偏兒子不學好，在學校打架鬧事，慘遭學校退學。葉問只好接受弟子李小龍的邀請，去美國為兒子申請學校，豈知華人到了美國受盡歧視，處處碰壁。<br />\n<br />\n李小龍於美國出書，收鬼佬徒弟教功夫，引起唐人街華人武術界不滿。李小龍因此得罪了中華總會會長萬宗華。葉問與萬會長相識之初，因為對於中華傳統武術意見不合，隨即展開了一場詠春對戰太極的戲碼，萬會長發現葉問受傷了，直接收起一隻手跟對方打。<br />\n<br />\n葉問拿不到萬會長的推薦信，無法讓兒子葉正入學。人在異鄉的葉問很想聽到兒子的聲音，可是每次的長途電話都被兒子拒絕接聽，父子關係惡劣。<br />\n<br />\n這時，李小龍的美軍徒弟吳建豪，想將詠春引入美國部隊，受空手道教官打壓，派人去唐人街踢館，被葉問狠狠教訓，挑起了美國海軍陸戰隊跟唐人街的仇恨。<br />\n<br />\n美國軍官趁著中秋晚會把會長綁走，並且打趴了所有會中的武師，找移民局拉人。這時葉問出馬，打趴了挑釁的美國人，美國人又把會長綁入海軍陸戰隊，並且打到重傷。葉問看不下去，認為中國人不能再被欺侮，於是叫吳建豪把他帶入海軍陸戰隊，美國人跟葉問一番激戰之後，再度打趴美國人。<br />\n<br />\n葉問解救了中華總會的貌美女兒若男，但還是無法讓萬宗華會長點頭寫推薦信。<br />\n<br />\n於是，葉問放棄了兒子的留學計劃，決定回香港並與兒子和好，教授兒子葉正畢生絕學，還叫他兒子用機器拍攝。最後，葉問在79歲因癌症去世，畫面切換至徒弟李小龍祭拜，然後開始播放前幾集畫面，包括洪金寶、黃曉明、熊黛林等場景。全劇完。<br />\n<br />\n#不是劇透<br />\n#不要share<br />\n#share了觀眾便不會購票"},{"pid":"68187efb9c5158fdb61bd4408f3f8fd5663e61d1","tid":1792361,"uid":331949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T14:56:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">好想瘋狂同佢玩膽機！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"977d3c1a674c8cdcb081ade1f92f48b02d4fba72","tid":1792361,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T14:59:38.000Z","msg":"幫手推下先"},{"pid":"8504d52420d588ee504296e45c55259ecc3977b4","tid":1792361,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T15:04:12.000Z","msg":"李漢民.jpg"},{"pid":"c5f1517712172d9e0f7ab6af891c06d670e26277","tid":1792361,"uid":44175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T01:02:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"f5e18393ea961230122921c69e93bb95dc44d6d0","tid":1792361,"uid":82068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T01:29:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FfhVure.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFfhVure.png&h=d72503c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uzdp7cU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuzdp7cU.png&h=e135a74a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0701ce8f56eaf033c97e3f0ccfec8b8441b5d118","tid":1792361,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf0745aa0ea1fbcaebebd418ae9f2d99aa84ac84","tid":1792361,"uid":147916,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T14:53:36.000Z","msg":"葉問生canncer，去美國幫仔搵學校，打贏晒班歧視支那人嘅鬼佬，同時李小龍既徒弟係美國得罪軍官，但軍官挑葉問機但打輸左，最後葉問返香港教仔詠春然後死咗。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T02:08:49.000Z","msg":"不推啦唔該"},{"pid":"b03f3df89e75534d9443f049e001e977ca4ca1d5","tid":1792361,"uid":59242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T02:52:54.000Z","msg":"咩叫我便判左出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />隻揪有外判？"}]}